dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:51:22.000Z","msg":"唔係冇事，佢著左草<br />\n<br />\n摩西好軟弱，但係神比佢一次又一次經歷，增強佢既信心，然而摩西又一次一次軟弱，但係佢見識到神係靠得住既，可以憑神而得力量。<br />\n<br />\n呢個見證要講既係神唔在乎我哋幾軟弱，佢要我哋靠佢得力，完成佢既事工。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:01:02.000Z","msg":"btw, 左膠係聖經中係法利賽人，用「規則」、「道理」謀殺他人既人，耶穌好唔妥佢哋。個思想模式同魯迅講中國五千年食人歷史既「食人者」差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死跟「常規」而漠視人性，例子有愛玻璃大聯盟主席林鄭月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9be990aed13476f6d2517e063a2e7c77eb04282","tid":1646241,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:02:05.000Z","msg":"你 罰抄聖經舊約 加新約 一次!"},{"pid":"ac09c16dee11dc60f365c983253b60744886e97d","tid":1646241,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad3c4a6dbccb33e00b0d3abc508c5912ef943b17","tid":1646241,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dea7430645e120fe76608bd1b122a15c3c55a5","tid":1646241,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddaddebefb446b045ff83e76ae9c7ea42cdfe9df","tid":1646241,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac48c22c5c0786f4c90346b050b367496b57ae18","tid":1646241,"uid":44171,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"摩西仲係麻包袋先鋒, 殺長子之災<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:58:37.000Z","msg":"耶和華先係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:07:36.000Z","msg":"耶和華係神, 摩西係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17a6c324bc1296887aa3ddd77b4da3f5757d30c","tid":1646